    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Die mercurii qui fuit decimus intrantis mensis aprelis, <rs
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum virorum</rs> presentia quorum
                        nomina inferius scripta invenientur. <persName key="#Marquis/duke #Houses"
                            ref="#people/3571">Albertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchio et dux</rs> investivit dompnum <persName
                            key="#Priors" ref="#people/3570">Wilielmum</persName>
                        <rs key="#Priors">priorem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Priors #Abbots #Abbots"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, quod est
                        scitum in <rs key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Dioecesis #Mother_churches">aepiscopatu</rs><geogName
                            key="#Comitatus" ref="#estates/2000">
                            <placeName key="#Comitatus #Dioecesis #Mother_churches"
                                ref="#places/275">Mantuano</placeName></geogName>, inter <rs
                            key="#Rivers">flumen</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Rivers">Padi</placeName> et <placeName key="#Rivers"
                            >Larionis</placeName>, adstante ibi dompno <persName key="#Abbots"
                            >Ogerio</persName>, <rs key="#Missus">vice</rs> dompni <persName
                            key="#Abbots" ref="#people/3568">Haeinrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots #Missus">abbatis</rs> ipsius monastetii et totius
                        congregationis, de tota illa <placeName key="#Forests" ref="#places/4194">
                            <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs> de Casteniolo</placeName> qua in se
                        retinuerat cum priorem investitura eidem monasterio de parte eiusdem silve
                        fecerat, infra istas coherentias, scilicet: a mane iuris ipsius monasterii,
                        a sera <rs key="#Canals">fossatum</rs>, quod factum est ab ipso monasterio
                        ab arzine antiquo usque in flumen Padi Vetuli ad dividendam silvam ipsius
                        marchionis a silva ipsius monasterii, a meridie iuris ipsius monasterii et
                        arzinis predictus usque in iamdictum fossatum novum, a septemtrione flumen
                        predicti Padi. Tali modo hanc investituram fecit ut liceat dompno abbati
                        eiusque fratribus eorumque successoribus de silva illa quicquid voluerint
                        facere ad eorum usum et utilitatem in perpetuum sine contraditione ipsius
                        marchionis et haeredum eius, sicut in <rs key="#Ordinatio">cartula prioris
                            investiture</rs> legitur. Actum est hoc in loco <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Churches" ref="#places/2967">Bondeno</placeName>, in <rs
                            key="#Houses">casa</rs> ipsius marchionis, iuxta <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName>Sancti Iacobi</orgName>. Anno dominice incarnationis millesimo
                        centesimo vigesimo nono, predicto die, inditione septima. <rs key="#Witness"
                            >Interfuerunt</rs> ibi: <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness"
                            >Wibertus</persName> de <placeName>Castello Agirani</placeName>,
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Wibertus</persName> de
                            <placeName>Erberia</placeName>, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Girardus</persName> filius
                            <persName>Girardi</persName> filii <persName>Bosonis</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Boso Longus</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness">Inricus</persName> de
                        Bondeno, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #Witness #Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"
                            >Albertus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldius</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus" ref="#places/34">Piguniaga</placeName>,
                        qui misit ipsum priorem in possessione predicte silve iussu ipsius
                        marchionis. (SN) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Bonus"
                                >Bonus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> sacri palacii his interfui, rogatus <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
